{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/BufferedInputStreamRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/BufferedInputStreamRef\/InputStreamProtocol-Implementations"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Closes the stream, releasing resources related to it."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"close","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"cancellable","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","text":"CancellableRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil) "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Once the stream is closed, all other operations will return "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"closed"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Closing a stream multiple times will not return an error."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Streams will be automatically closed when the last reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is dropped, but you might want to call this function to make sure","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resources are released as early as possible."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Some streams might keep the backing store of the stream (e.g. a file descriptor)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"open after the stream is closed. See the documentation for the individual","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"stream for details."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"On failure the first error that happened will be reported, but the close","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"operation will finish as much as possible. A stream that failed to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"close will still return "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"closed"},{"type":"text","text":" for all operations. Still, it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is important to check and report the error to the user."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"text":" is not ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", then the operation can be cancelled by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"was cancelled, the error ","type":"text"},{"code":"cancelled","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be returned."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Cancelling a close will still leave the stream closed, but some streams","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"can use a faster close that doesn’t block to e.g. check errors.","type":"text"}]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/BufferedInputStreamRef\/close(cancellable:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"extendedModule":"GIO","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:3GIO19InputStreamProtocolPAAE5close11cancellableSbAA14CancellableRefVSg_tKF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO22BufferedInputStreamRefV","title":"close(cancellable:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"close"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","text":"CancellableRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"?) "},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/bufferedinputstreamref\/close(cancellable:)"]}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/BufferedInputStreamRef/InputStreamProtocol-Implementations":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/BufferedInputStreamRef\/InputStreamProtocol-Implementations","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/bufferedinputstreamref\/inputstreamprotocol-implementations","abstract":[],"title":"InputStreamProtocol Implementations","type":"topic","role":"collectionGroup","kind":"article"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/CancellableRef":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"CancellableRef","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"CancellableRef","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/cancellableref","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GCancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" allows operations to be cancelled."}],"title":"CancellableRef"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/FilterInputStream":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FilterInputStream","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/filterinputstream","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Base class for input stream implementations that perform some"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"kind of filtering operation on a base stream. Typical examples","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"of filtering operations are character set conversion, compression"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and byte order flipping.","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"FilterInputStream","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"FilterInputStream","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"FilterInputStream"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/BufferedInputStreamRef":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"BufferedInputStreamRef","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"BufferedInputStreamRef","abstract":[{"text":"Buffered input stream implements [class","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FilterInputStream","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"] and provides"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"for buffered reads."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"BufferedInputStreamRef","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/BufferedInputStreamRef","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/bufferedinputstreamref"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/BufferedInputStreamRef/close(cancellable:)":{"type":"topic","title":"close(cancellable:)","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/bufferedinputstreamref\/close(cancellable:)","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/BufferedInputStreamRef\/close(cancellable:)","abstract":[{"text":"Closes the stream, releasing resources related to it.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"close"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"CancellableRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"?) "},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"